@Node Usage "Usage"

  Usage
  =====

    Start the door from the BBS prompt by typing "B" and pressing
    return.

    Or:

    type in "B" followed by a space and then the name of a bulletin to have
    that bulletin displayed.

    You can call this door from screen files like this:

    @^USERDOOR^B@

    or say you wanted to display a bulletin called "Lamers" you could do this

    @^USERDOOR^B Lamers@

    Don't forget that you can different bulletins for different conferences
    and nodes by changing the screen files in screens/bulletins and
    screens/special!

    Yet another kewl feature of HydraBBS!

@EndNode



